Finding: CAR-01 is raised and successfully closed.

Opinion: The verification team confirms;

The monitoring plan has been implemented as per the registered PD /05/;

The monitoring complies with the requirement of the applied methodology /07/;

The information inflow (from data generation, aggregation, to recording, calculation and reporting) is included above under each parameters and confirms to the requirement of the PDD;

The values included in the monitoring report and corresponding emission reduction sheets are verified and included under each monitoring parameter, wherever appropriate;

